title: Raiders’ Sebastian Janikowski has a leg up on history
text:
Photo: Ben Margot, AP FILE - In this Aug. 14, 2015, file photo, Oakland Raiders place kicker Sebastian Janikowski (11) watches from the sidelines during an NFL preseason football game against the St. Louis Rams in Oakland, Calif. Janikowski is about to set the franchise record for games played with No. 241 Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, against Denver. FILE - In this Aug. 14, 2015, file photo, Oakland Raiders place...
With 240 games down ... who knows how many more to go?
